<div class="content-body">
    <h1>Feed Options</h1>
    <p>Subscribe to my blog using one of these feed formats:</p>

    <div class="feed-options">
        <div class="feed-option">
            <h3>RSS Feed</h3>
            <p>
                Traditional RSS 2.0 format, compatible with most feed readers.
            </p>
            <a href="/feed.rss" class="feed-link">Subscribe to RSS</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feed-option">
            <h3>Atom Feed</h3>
            <p>
                Modern Atom 1.0 format, more feature-rich and
                standards-compliant.
            </p>
            <a href="/feed.atom" class="feed-link">Subscribe to Atom</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feed-info">
        <h3>How to use these feeds:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Copy the feed URL</strong> from one of the links above
            </li>
            <li><strong>Paste it into your feed reader</strong></li>
            <li>
                <strong>Or use a browser extension</strong> like RSS Feed Reader
            </li>
            <li><strong>Get notified</strong> when I publish new posts</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
